#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-30-poetry-vs-rye.rst:72
msgid "**Pythonバージョンの自前管理** ："
msgstr "**Manage your own Python version**:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-30-poetry-vs-rye.rst:74
msgid "``rye pin 3.12`` でそのバージョンを直接DLして使うため、 ``pyenv`` や ``asdf`` は不要です。"
msgstr ""
"You don't need ``pyenv`` or ``asdf`` because you can directly download and "
"use that version with ``rye pin 3.12``."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-30-poetry-vs-rye.rst:76
msgid "**高速な依存解決** ："
msgstr "**Fast dependency resolution**:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-30-poetry-vs-rye.rst:78
msgid "``uv`` を利用しており、Poetryより桁違いに高速です。"
msgstr "It uses ``uv`` and is orders of magnitude faster than Poetry."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-30-poetry-vs-rye.rst:80
msgid "**シンプルな設計と統合CLI**  ："
msgstr "**Simple design and integrated CLI**:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-30-poetry-vs-rye.rst:82
msgid ""
"``rye fmt`` （フォーマット）、 ``rye lint`` （静的解析）、 ``rye test`` "
"（テスト実行）など、開発で使う基本的な機能をすべて内包。"
msgstr ""
"Contains all the basic functions used in development, such as ``rye fmt`` "
"(format), ``rye lint`` (static analysis), and ``rye test`` (test execution)."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-30-poetry-vs-rye.rst:84
msgid "**自己更新コマンド** ："
msgstr "**Self-update command**:"

